          <content>Deployment Pattern
----------------------------------
Pattern: Single VPS + Docker
Reverse Proxy: Nginx
Database: PostgreSQL (host)
Container Runtime: Docker
Persistence: Bind Mounts
SSL: Nginx (Let's Encrypt)</content>
